{"tid":151531,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)星夢動物園 3X反恐暴族1-3","createTime":"2017-03-11T02:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T08:40:55.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"727854e987689442d5916cc00f63bae501b10119","tid":151531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T02:58:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c50c2d92\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5333600b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/84/Sing-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F84%2FSing-poster.jpg&h=c8be829b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/78/XXx_Return_of_Xander_Cage_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F78%2FXXx_Return_of_Xander_Cage_Poster.jpg&h=4b8400dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事的主角是巴斯特穆恩，他是一隻風度翩翩、口若懸河的無尾熊，曾經經營一家金碧輝煌、高朋滿座的劇場，但是現在卻窮途潦倒、門可羅雀。巴斯特穆恩永遠都是這麼開朗樂觀，充滿了正能量，但是有些人卻認為他根本就是在自欺欺人，不肯面對現實，不過他仍然熱愛他的劇場，而且為了不讓劇場關門倒閉，不管做什麼他都願意。但是當他的熱誠和野心即將受到致命打擊的時候，他只剩最後一次機會讓他的劇場再度成為藝能界最高的殿堂，他必須舉辦一場全世界最盛大的歌唱選秀大賽...<br />\n<br />\n2.桑德&middot;凱吉（馮&middot;迪索）是一個愛好極限運動的男人，他被星探奧古斯都&middot;吉本斯（塞繆爾&middot;L&middot;傑克遜）發掘後，推薦到了美國國家安全局做了一個特工。經過刻苦的訓練之後，凱吉被派往捷克首都布拉格刺殺犯罪分子尤里<br />\n<br />\n3.延續第一集的動作冒險、極限運動風格，Ice Cube飾演的壞小子，一向喜歡挑戰威權與極限，而在被迫成為美國中情局探員後，秘密前往華府.. <br />\n<br />\n4.故事敘述從極限運動員變成政府特工的桑德&middot;凱吉本被認為已死亡，但因致命戰士翔與他的團隊企圖利用危險的潘多拉盒子為非作歹，使得桑德&middot;凱吉再次被找上，組成新團隊來阻止；而他也發現自己將陷入世界各國政府高層間的勾結和陰謀中..<br />\n<br />\n11 25AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcdd00d982de584b7200948658b1f4171168aba","tid":151531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T03:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c36aa052fb2e6cf284bed4aef4c5e25027de390","tid":151531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325ef75c03916f38b846185f70a9800587680897","tid":151531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T04:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b970079ba88255644fea807bfc353c695fd196d1","tid":151531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac8ec12b8f3049fbe18ff66e70aa5de3b3d0d00","tid":151531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a5322ecb93c41bc3683977d58332d95c24be3e","tid":151531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s